UID:ai1ec-3927@writersguildbloomington.com
DTSTAMP:20260309T020723Z
CATEGORIES:
CONTACT:
DESCRIPTION:Poetry Matters at Morgenstern’s\nwill feature Lisa Kwong\n \n\n
 Lisa is a Bloomington writer and poet who teaches at Indiana University an
 d Ivy Tech Community College.\nCome hear her read from her book Becoming A
 ppalAsian (Glass Lyre Press).\nHer reading will be followed by a conversat
 ion about her book\, poetry\, writing\, and anything else that catches her
  fancy.\nThe event will take place at Morgenstern Books in the back at the
  conference table.\nThe store will have copies of his book for sale prior 
 to and during the event.\nHope to see you there!
