BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:ai1ec-3917@writersguildbloomington.com
DTSTAMP:20260309T020723Z
CATEGORIES:
CONTACT:
DESCRIPTION:Constellation Stage & Screen\npresents\nAmerican Fast\n\n a Riv
 eting New Sports Drama\n\nby Kareen Fahmy\n\n on stage March 23 – April 8
 \n at the Ted Jones Playhouse\n\n\nCollege basketball superstar Khady Sala
 ma dreams of leading her team to the NCAA Championship.\nBut in her senior
  year\, March Madness coincides with Ramadan and she’s promised her devout
  mother that she’ll fast.\nWhen her story goes public\, Khady unexpectedly
  becomes a role model for young Muslim women everywhere\, with just one sm
 all problem…she’s lying about fasting.\nAs the tournament unfolds\, Khady 
 is forced to grapple with her faith\, family\, and what it means to win at
  all costs.\n\nFor a detailed performance schedule\, please visit our webs
 ite. Learn more and find tickets at https://seeconstellation.org/mainstage
 /american-fast/
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20230323T164100
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20230408T174100
LOCATION:Ted Jones Playhouse
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:American Fast  by Kareen Fahmy
