CATEGORIES:
CONTACT:
DESCRIPTION:Constellation Stage & Screen presents\n\nDon’t Let the Pigeon D
 rive the Bus! The Musical!\n\non stage April 28 – May 14 at the Waldron Ar
 ts Center!\n\nWhatever you do\, don’t let the Pigeon star in his own music
 al production! It’s not easy being the Pigeon – you never get to do ANYTHI
 NG! But when the Bus Driver has a crisis that threatens to make her passen
 gers (gasp!) late\, maybe that wily bird CAN do something. Featuring an in
 novative mix of songs\, and feathers\, Don’t Let the Pigeon Drive the Bus!
  The Musical! is sure to get everyone’s wings flapping.\n\nConstellation i
 s featuring a sensory-friendly performance on Sunday\, May 14 at 4:00pm. C
 lick here to learn more accomodations at this special performance.\n\nFor 
 a detailed performance schedule\, please visit our website. \nLearn more a
 nd find tickets at https://seeconstellation.org/kids/pigeon
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20230428T160000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20230514T173000
LOCATION:John Waldron Arts Center
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Don’t Let the Pigeon Drive the Bus! The Musical!
