X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC '-//W3C//DTD HTML 3.2//E
 N'>\\n<HTML>\\n<HEAD>\\n<TITLE></TITLE>\\n</HEAD>\\n<BODY><div>\n<h3 style
 ='text-align: center\;'>Constellation Stage & Screen presents</h3>\n<div s
 tyle='text-align: center\;'></div>\n<h1 style='text-align: center\;'><i>Do
 n’t Let the Pigeon Drive the Bus! The Musical!</i></h1>\n<div style='text-
 align: center\;'></div>\n<div style='text-align: center\;'>on stage April 
 28 – May 14 at the Waldron Arts Center!</div>\n<div style='text-align: cen
 ter\;'></div>\n<div style='text-align: center\;'>Whatever you do\, don’t l
 et the Pigeon star in his own musical production! It’s not easy being the 
 Pigeon – you never get to do ANYTHING! But when the Bus Driver has a crisi
 s that threatens to make her passengers (gasp!) late\, maybe that wily bir
 d CAN do something. Featuring an innovative mix of songs\, and feathers\, 
 <i>Don’t Let the Pigeon Drive the Bus! The Musical!</i> is sure to get eve
 ryone’s wings flapping.</div>\n<div style='text-align: center\;'></div>\n<
 div style='text-align: center\;'>Constellation is featuring a sensory-frie
 ndly performance on Sunday\, May 14 at 4:00pm. Click <a href='https://seec
 onstellation.org/kids/pigeon' target='_blank' rel='nofollow noopener noref
 errer'>here</a> to learn more accomodations at this special performance.</
 div>\n<div style='text-align: center\;'></div>\n<h3 style='text-align: cen
 ter\;'><span style='color: #993300\;'><em><strong>For a detailed performan
 ce schedule\, please visit our website</strong></em>. </span></h3>\n<div s
 tyle='text-align: center\;'><strong>Learn more and find tickets at <a href
 ='https://seeconstellation.org/kids/pigeon' target='_blank' rel='nofollow 
