 October 20 – November 5 at the Waldron Arts Center!\n\nEveryone’s favorite
  mischievous monkey and “The Man in the Yellow Hat” spring to life in this
  adventure-filled musical. Join Curious George\,\nthe inquisitive\, lovabl
 e monkey – star of books\, movies\, and the award-winning PBS television s
 how – as he goes on a mission to save the Golden Meatball Contest in Rome!
 \nThis musical story of encouragement\, determination and selfless love wi
 ll warm hearts and tummies alike.\n\n*Sensory-Friendly Performance on Sund
 ay\, November 5 at 4:00pm*\n\nFor a detailed performance schedule\, please
  visit our website. Learn more and find tickets at https://seeconstellatio
 n.org/kids/curious-george/
