 g> is the first female Poet Laureate of Lucas County\, Ohio. Her most rece
 nt chapbook\, Semidomesticated (re-released by Sheila-Na-Gig Editions\, 20
 22) won Red Flag Poetry’s 2020 chapbook contest. Her prior chapbooks are B
 eyond the Sidewalk (Nightballet Press\, 2017) and Not All Who Are Lost Wan
 der (Finishing Line Press\, 2016). She is poetry editor at Of Rust and Gla
 ss\, Membership Chair at Ohio Poetry Association\, and hosts a monthly rea
