DESCRIPTION:Coffee With Friends\nwith\nHeather Ray & Ken Keffer\nSunday\, N
 ovember 12\, 2023 2:00 PM – 3:00 PM\nDowntown Library Meeting Room 1B\nIn 
 this interactive presentation\, Ken Keffer and Heather Ray\, owners of Wil
 d Birds Unlimited\, will feature nature hotspots in Bloomington and discus
 s phenology through the seasons. Learn about the endangered whooping crane
 s that winter in Goose Pond Wildlife Area\, and why goldfinches are such l
 ate summer nesters. Ken and Heather will provide information on the best p
 laces to see and experience Bloomington’s beautiful nature scene while dis
 cussing their books\, 100 Things to Do in Bloomington Before You Die and K
 nowing the Trees: Discovering the Forest from Seed to Snag. Age 12 and up.
 \n 
