 .com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/lynch.png 836w' sizes='auto\, (max-width: 
 191px) 100vw\, 191px' /></a></p>\n<p style='text-align: center\;'><strong>
 Antonia Matthew</strong> was born in England before World War II. Her radi
 o play\, “Antonia’s Homefront” built around the letters she received from 
 her father in Burma during WWII has recently been produced on WFHB By Rich
