 berger-768x1024.jpg 768w\, https://writersguildbloomington.com/wp-content/
 uploads/2023/11/rensberger.jpg 810w' sizes='auto\, (max-width: 225px) 100v
 w\, 225px' /></a></p>\n<p style='text-align: center\;'><strong>Shana Ritte
 r’s</strong> poetry and short stories have appeared in various journals an
 d magazines including Lilith\, Fifth Wednesday and Georgetown Review. Her 
