CONTACT:
DESCRIPTION:Constellation Stage & Screen\npresents\nRoald Dahl’s\nMatilda t
 he Musical\n\n\nThis holiday season\, Constellation Stage & Screen present
 s Matilda the Musical\, on stage December 14-31 at the Buskirk-Chumley The
 ater!\n\nFrom the visionary mind of Roald Dahl comes the Tony Award-winnin
 g Matilda the Musical! Matilda Wormwood is a gifted little girl armed with
  a sharp mind\, a vivid imagination\, and a love of books. Misunderstood b
 y her cruel and unloving family\, she is thrilled to begin school. Only on
 e problem – the school is run by Miss Trunchbull\, the evil headmistress w
 ho terrorizes the students with her strict discipline. Matilda soon takes 
 a stand to defend her friends from Trunchbull’s wrath and outwit her unkin
 d parents. Packed with high-energy dance numbers and astonishing stage mag
 ic\, children and adults alike will be thrilled and delighted by the story
  of this extraordinary little girl!\n\nFor a detailed performance schedule
 \, please visit our website. Learn more and find tickets at https://seecon
 stellation.org/kids/matilda/
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20231214T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20231231T140000
