 e—Professor Emerita\, Indiana University—is a storyteller\, actor\, and wr
 iter. She has written four original plays\, numerous one-person shows\, an
 d a book—<strong>Come Sit with Me: Life in Poetry\, Prose\, and Plays</str
 ong>. Gladys is co-founder of Resilience Productions INC\, a theatrical co
 mpany that researches\, writes\, and produces plays—inspired by actual eve
 nts—that tell the African American story.</p>\n<p style='text-align: cente
 r\;'>Gladys DeVane’s book\, <strong>Come Sit with Me: Life in Poetry\, Pro
 se\, and Plays</strong>\, will be available for sale. Cash and checks acce
