 ign: center\;'>Beau Vallance is retired from art-museum work and IU teache
 r education. Her writing lately has been for a summer newspaper in Michiga
 n\, the IU Emeriti House life-writing workshop\, a year-long StoryWorth pr
 oject\, two pieces in The Ryder\, very long emails to friends\, and a draf
 t of her own obituary. Her writing has gotten quite free-wheeling since sh
 e’s no longer writing for professional journals\, but she had a huge resum
 e of articles on such exciting topics as the hidden curriculum\, curriculu
 m theory\, and museum education. It’s more fun now.</p>\n</BODY></HTML>
