UID:ai1ec-4501@writersguildbloomington.com
DTSTAMP:20260309T020724Z
CATEGORIES:
CONTACT:
DESCRIPTION:Second Thursday Spoken Word Series\nStaged Reading\na new Mervy
 n Alphonse play\nThe Deeper You Dig\n \n \nA staged reading by Writers Gui
 ld members Zilia Balkasky-Sellés\, Joan Hawkins\, Peter Kaczmarczyk\, Shay
 ne Laughter\, Erin Strole\, and Eric Zobel.\nAn undercover Police officer 
 finds herself in wildly uncharted territory when an assignment takes her b
 ack to a traumatic past and to a personal identity that she had hoped to p
 ermanently put behind her. Much of the play take place in prison.\nEvent b
 y Writers Guild at Bloomington and Tony Brewer\nFree and open to the publi
 c\nBEER & WINE available for purchase\nTHURSDAY\, AUG 8\n6pm\nBackspace Ga
 llery\, inside Bonne Fête\, 112 West 6th Street\, on the square in Bloomin
 gton IN\nSponsored in part by the Indiana Arts Commission\, Bloomington Ar
 ts Commission\, and the Bloomington Urban Enterprise Association\n 
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20240808T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20240808T200000
