 N'>\\n<HTML>\\n<HEAD>\\n<TITLE></TITLE>\\n</HEAD>\\n<BODY><p><a href='http
 s://writersguildbloomington.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/WG-spoken-word-
 series.jpg'><img loading='lazy' decoding='async' class=' wp-image-4502 ali
 gnleft' src='https://writersguildbloomington.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/0
 7/WG-spoken-word-series-300x232.jpg' alt='' width='325' height='251' srcse
 t='https://writersguildbloomington.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/WG-spoke
 n-word-series-300x232.jpg 300w\, https://writersguildbloomington.com/wp-co
 ntent/uploads/2024/07/WG-spoken-word-series-1024x791.jpg 1024w\, https://w
