CONTACT:
DESCRIPTION:Off Night Productions presents \nSteel Magnolias\nAugust 11 & 1
 8 at 2pm\nAugust 12\, 13\, 19\, 20 at 7pm\nWaldron Auditorium\, downtown B
 loomington.\n \nStep into the glittery\, glamorous sanctuary of Truvy’s be
 auty salon in 1980s Chinquapin\, Louisiana\, where six of the town’s most 
 beloved women share jokes\, advice\, and unwavering support. This hilariou
 s and touching tale showcases the power of female friendship to keep us la
 ughing and inspire us to face life’s toughest moments.\nStarring local art
 ists including Greta Lind\, Maria Walker\, and Maggie Lyn Held!\nTickets a
 re on sale now through the Buskirk-Chumley Box Office. Find tickets and le
 arn more at https://offnightproductions.org/\n 
