DESCRIPTION: \n \nThe Writers Guild at Bloomington presents \nLast Sunday P
 oetry\nFeaturing Indiana poets JL Kato and John Hinton\n \n \nJL KATO is t
 he 2022 Indiana Literary Champion\, whose Shadows Set in Concrete was sele
 cted the 2011 Best Indiana Book of Poetry by the Indiana Center for the Bo
 ok.\nJOHN HINTON is the author of two poetry collections\, Blackbird Songs
 \, and Held. As president of Poetry Society of Indiana\, Hinton has led nu
 merous poetry workshops to enable participants to tap into their creative 
 potential. He has also hosted open mics throughout the state of Indiana.\n
  \n8/25/24 Sunday\n7:00 – 8:30 PM\nMorgenstern’s Bookstore & Cafe\n 
