CATEGORIES:
CONTACT:
DESCRIPTION:Click here to see the video of this event: Juniper Art Gallery 
 youtube video \nThanks to Duane Busick for recording the event\nJoin the W
 riters Guild for a very special reading in honor of National Literacy Mont
 h!\n \n \nEnglish learners from VITAL at the Monroe County Public Library 
 will share their words and stories.\nThese learners come from Peru\, China
 \, South Korea\, Egypt\, Iran\, Brazil\, and Taiwan.\nCome for a fun after
 noon!!\nOpen Mic to follow.\nSunday\, September 1\, 2024\nThe Juniper Art 
 Gallery and Cafe\n615 W. Kirkwood Ave.\n4pm to 5:30pm  Please note the new
  start time of 4pm! \nPlease no outside food or drink! 
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20240901T160000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20240901T173000
