 N'>\\n<HTML>\\n<HEAD>\\n<TITLE></TITLE>\\n</HEAD>\\n<BODY><p>As a daughter
  of Southern Appalachia\, Writer Guild of Bloomington Member Lisa Kwong wi
 ll be participating in a Zoom event called <a href='https://events.humanit
 ix.com/soul-waters-rising-an-appalachian-pause'>Soul Waters Rising: An App
 alachian Pause</a> on Wednesday\, October 30\, to raise funds for Hurrican
 e Helene relief. <a href='https://events.humanitix.com/soul-waters-rising-
 an-appalachian-pause/tickets'>This is a link for tickets on a sliding scal
