 'lazy' decoding='async' class='alignleft  wp-image-4560' src='https://writ
 ersguildbloomington.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-thumbnail_image.p
 ng' alt='' width='116' height='163' /><i></i></div>\n<div><i> </i></div>\n
 <div>\n<div>\n<p>A professional writer since 1995\, <strong>Susan</strong>
  has written for the Boy Scouts\, stoners\, interventional radiologists\, 
 would-be beekeepers\, depressives\, the 1%\, and many others. Her nonficti
 on work appears in <em>Hobby Farms Magazine</em>\, <em>Bloom Magazin</em>e
