 uate of Indiana University. In addition to writing\, he paints\, draws\, c
 ooks\, sings and plays guitar and flute. He and his wife\, Ann\, love to t
 ravel and call San Miguel de Allende in Mexico their second home.</p>\n<p>
 November 3\, 2024<br />\n4-5:30pm<br />\nThe Juniper Art Gallery and Cafe<
