 A live broadcast performance features audio theatre plays and comedy sketc
 hes by the Mighty Firehouse Art Players\, music from Kid Kazooey and the F
 our-Alarm Orchestra\, special musical guest Krista Detor\, and poetry crea
 ted by Indiana’s Literary Champion\, Tony Brewer. The audience becomes par
 t of the two-hour show at the Waldron Auditorium\, starting at 2 p.m. Nove
 mber 17\, so come and join us! The Follies webpage is https://wfhb.org/cat
 egory/arts-entertainment/follies/\n\nBroadcast and streamed live over WFHB
 \, 91.3 FM and http://www.wfhb.org.  Live Streams:\nhttps://wfhb.org/liste
 n/\nhttp://www.radiorethink.com/listen/wfhb\nhttp://radio.garden/listen/bl
