 ory power on checks.</p>\n<p>d) <em>Secretary:</em> Keeps minutes of board
  meetings and makes them available to the<br />\nmembership. Keeps adminis
 trative\, meeting\, and membership records.</p>\n<p>e)  <em>Terms & Limits
 : </em> Board Members will serve until the end of December of the year<br 
 />\nthey were voted into their position. Board members will serve one-year
  terms\, and may<br />\nserve five (5) consecutive terms.  Additional term
 s in the same position may be served<br />\nafter a one-year absence from 
 the Board position.</p>\n<p>f)  Board members are required to attend at le
 ast sixty percent of all business meetings.<br />\nAny board member who ca
 nnot make this commitment will not be eligible for election<br />\nthe fol
 lowing year.</p>\n</BODY></HTML>
