 essor emeritus at Purdue University\, Fort Wayne\, and 2014 – 2016 poet la
 ureate of Indiana.\n \n \n2/23/25\, 7-8:30 PM (EST)\nMorgenstern’s Books &
  Cafe\, 849 S Auto Mall Rd\, Bloomington IN 47401\n 
