 png'><img loading='lazy' decoding='async' class='alignleft size-medium wp-
 image-4668' src='https://writersguildbloomington.com/wp-content/uploads/20
 25/02/maple-and-vine-300x300.png' alt='' width='300' height='300' srcset='
