 ine-300x300.png 300w\, https://writersguildbloomington.com/wp-content/uplo
 ads/2025/02/maple-and-vine-1024x1024.png 1024w\, https://writersguildbloom
 ington.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/maple-and-vine-150x150.png 150w\, ht
 tps://writersguildbloomington.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/maple-and-vin
 e-768x768.png 768w\, https://writersguildbloomington.com/wp-content/upload
 s/2025/02/maple-and-vine-270x270.png 270w\, https://writersguildbloomingto
 n.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/maple-and-vine-230x230.png 230w\, https:/
 /writersguildbloomington.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/maple-and-vine.png
  1080w' sizes='auto\, (max-width: 300px) 100vw\, 300px' /></a><span style=
 'color: #008000\;'><strong><em>Welcome to the corner of Maple and Vine\, w
 here every day is 1955! </em></strong></span></p>\n<h6><em><span style='co
 lor: #ff99cc\;'><strong>Constellation Stage & Screen presents</strong> </s
 pan></em></h6>\n<h1 style='text-align: center\;'><span style='color: #0080
 00\;'><strong>Maple and Vine</strong></span></h1>\n<h6><em><strong><span s
 tyle='color: #ff99cc\;'>March 27 – April 13 </span></strong></em></h6>\n<h
 6><em><strong><span style='color: #ff99cc\;'>at the Constellation Playhous
 e in downtown Bloomington</span></strong></em></h6>\n<p>Katha and Ryu have
  become allergic to their 21st-century lives. When they meet a charismatic
  man from a community of 1950s re-enactors\, they decide to forsake cell p
 hones and DoorDash for cigarettes and Tupperware parties. But after moving
  to this compulsively authentic world\, Katha and Ryu are surprised by wha
 t their new neighbors – and they themselves – are willing to sacrifice for
  happiness.</p>\n<p>For showtimes\, tickets\, and more information\, visit
  <a href='https://seeconstellation.org/mainstage/maple-and-vine'>https://s
 eeconstellation.org/mainstage/maple-and-vine</a><br />\n*Featuring Pay Wha
 t You Will Thursdays*</p>\n</BODY></HTML>
