 0w' sizes='auto\, (max-width: 300px) 100vw\, 300px' /></a></p>\n<p style='
 text-align: left\;'><strong><em>Constellation Stage and Screen presents: <
 /em></strong></p>\n<div>\n<p><i>Mamma Mia! (2008): Sing Along </i>at the W
 aldron Auditorium in downtown Bloomington.</p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>C
 alling all dancing queens and super troupers! You’ll have a blast singing 
 along to hit songs from the popular 1970s group ABBA. This smash-hit movie
  musical\, based on the <a href='https://mamma-mia.com/' target='_blank' r
 el='noopener'>stage show of the same name</a>\, is the story of a bride-to
 -be trying to find her real father.</p>\n<p><b>Pre-Show Extravaganza:</b><
 br />\nBe sure to dress in your Mamma Mia best\, because we’re kicking off
  the screening with a costume contest! Show off your disco- and island-ins
 pired looks for the chance to win a fabulous prize. After the contest\, te
 st your <em>Mamma Mia</em> knowledge with a finish-that-lyric challenge! C
 ome early to take photos at our photo booth and grab a themed cocktail fro
 m the bar.</p>\n<p>Tickets On S</p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<p><strong>Saturday\, 
