X-WP-IMAGES-URL:thumbnail\;https://writersguildbloomington.com/wp-content/u
 ploads/2025/08/546214790_1189801246505830_8181105135888652863_n-300x189.jp
 g\;300\;189\,medium\;https://writersguildbloomington.com/wp-content/upload
