 y\, and welcomes members regardless of gender\, race\, sexual orientation\
 , religious affiliation\, and ability.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>7-8:30 PM (EST)<br 
 />\nMorgenstern Books & Cafe (849 S Auto Mall Rd\, Bloomington IN 47401)</
 p>\n</div>\n</BODY></HTML>
